CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `AdminBranchView`(IN P_CMD nvarchar(10), IN P_Id nvarchar(8), IN P_BranchName nvarchar(100), IN P_Description nvarchar(500), IN P_BranchImage nvarchar(8), IN P_FileName nvarchar(500), IN P_FilePath nvarchar(100), IN P_FileSize nvarchar(10)) BEGIN DECLARE V_ID nvarchar(8); IF (P_CMD = 'GET_ALL') THEN SELECT t.Id, t.BranchName, t.Description, t.BranchImage, t1.FileName FROM tblbranch t LEFT JOIN tblimagebranch t1 ON t.BranchImage = t1.Id; ELSEIF (P_CMD = 'GET_BID') THEN SELECT t.Id, t.BranchName, t.Description, t.BranchImage, t1.FileName FROM tblbranch t LEFT JOIN tblimagebranch t1 ON t.BranchImage = t1.Id WHERE t.Id = P_Id; ELSEIF (P_CMD = 'INSERT') THEN CALL GetRecordId('tblbranch', 1); SELECT t.LastId INTO V_ID FROM tblrecordid t WHERE t.RecordName = 'tblbranch'; INSERT INTO tblbranch (Id, BranchName, Description, BranchImage) VALUES (V_ID, P_BranchName, P_Description, P_BranchImage); ELSEIF (P_CMD = 'INSERTI') THEN CALL GetRecordId('tblimagebranch', 1); SELECT t.LastId INTO V_ID FROM tblrecordid t WHERE t.RecordName = 'tblimagebranch'; INSERT INTO tblimagebranch (Id, FileName, Type, FileSize) VALUES (V_ID, P_FileName, P_FilePath, P_FileSize);
ELSEIF (P_CMD = 'UPDATE') THEN IF (P_FileName = '') THEN UPDATE tblbranch t SET t.BranchName = P_BranchName, t.Description = P_Description -- t.BranchImage = P_BranchImage WHERE t.Id = P_Id; ELSE UPDATE tblbranch t SET t.BranchName = P_BranchName, t.Description = P_Description, t.BranchImage = P_BranchImage WHERE t.Id = P_Id; END IF; -- UPDATE tblbranch t -- SET t.BranchName = P_BranchName, -- t.Description = P_Description, -- t.BranchImage = P_BranchImage -- WHERE t.Id = P_Id; ELSEIF (P_CMD = 'DELETE') THEN DELETE FROM tblbranch WHERE Id = P_Id; ELSEIF (P_CMD = 'DELETEI') THEN DELETE FROM tblimagebranch WHERE Id = P_Id; ELSEIF (P_CMD = 'GET_FID') THEN SELECT t.LastId FROM tblrecordid t WHERE t.RecordName = 'tblimagebranch'; END IF; END

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `AdminCustomerView`(IN P_CMD nvarchar(10), IN P_Id nvarchar(8), IN P_LastName nvarchar(50), IN P_FirstName nvarchar(50), IN P_Gender nvarchar(1), IN P_DateOfBirth nvarchar(10), IN P_PhoneNumber nvarchar(10), IN P_Email nvarchar(250), IN P_JobTitle nvarchar(100), IN P_Country nvarchar(8), IN P_Province nvarchar(8), IN P_District nvarchar(8), IN P_Commnues nvarchar(8), IN P_Villages nvarchar(8), IN P_Street nvarchar(25), IN P_House nvarchar(10), IN P_Password nvarchar(250)) BEGIN IF (P_CMD = 'GET_ALL') THEN SELECT t.Id, CONCAT(t.LastName, ' ', t.FirstName) AS CusName, t.Gender, t.DateOfBirth, t.PhoneNumber, t.Email, t.JobTitle, CONCAT(cou.Country, ' ', pro.Province, ' ', dis.Distict, ' ', com.Communes, ' ', vil.Villages, ' ', t.Street, ' ', t.House) AS Address FROM tblcustomer t INNER JOIN tblcountry cou ON t.Country = cou.Id INNER JOIN tblprovinces pro ON t.Province = pro.Id LEFT JOIN tbldistricts dis ON t.District = dis.Id LEFT JOIN tblcommunes com ON t.Commnues = com.Id LEFT JOIN tblvillages vil ON t.Villages = vil.Id; ELSEIF (P_CMD = 'GET_CID') THEN SELECT t.Id, CONCAT(t.LastName, ' ', t.FirstName) AS CusName, t.Gender, t.DateOfBirth, t.PhoneNumber, t.Email, t.JobTitle, cou.Country, pro.Province, dis.Distict, com.Communes, vil.Villages, t.Street, t.House FROM tblcustomer t INNER JOIN tblcountry cou ON t.Country = cou.Id INNER JOIN tblprovinces pro ON t.Province = pro.Id LEFT JOIN tbldistricts dis ON t.District = dis.Id LEFT JOIN tblcommunes com ON t.Commnues = com.Id LEFT JOIN tblvillages vil ON t.Villages = vil.Id WHERE t.Id = P_Id;
